headline: 3 Top Dividend Stocks Yielding More Than 3% to Buy Right Now
summary: The dividend yield on the S&P 500 recently hit its lowest point in 20 years at less than 1.2%.  Brookfield Infrastructure (NYSE: BIPC)(NYSE: BIP), Rexford Industrial Realty (NYSE: REXR), and Mid-America Apartment Communities (NYSE: MAA) currently have dividend yields above 3%, making them great dividend stocks to buy right now.
